        <enum>(a)</enum>
        <header>Effective
			 date</header>
        <text>Except as provided in <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Bankruptcy Nondiscrimination Enhancement Act of 2013/s:3/ss:b" proposed="true">subsection (b)</cato:entity-ref>, this Act and the
